body: I found the English version doujin-moe.us

When I saw this posted here, I thought maybe it had FINALLY been TL'd. Ah well... It's simply a higher quality scan than the previously uploaded gallery. Which is great, of course, but, well... Then again, it's probably not difficult to figure out the general idea. ...At the end, I could easily imagine the text for Tabitha being something like this: "Dammit, she did it AGAIN!? Better get the mop and ammonia ready..." Prolly isn't what it says, but... I can see the sentiment being there.
